<br>
Furthermore sage Balic (word &amp; rune quest) never mentions what circles of power to use, so far everyone has tried level 49 and level 44 components but the actual components could be as low as level 16 components. Heck they could be a combination of level 34 &amp; 29 components because that adds up to 63. Fortunately low level components are often sold to vendors for cash so getting them shouldn't be too hard.<br>
<br>
<br>
Has anyone tried using Mojo Sticks or vendor potions in the sage box to see if it extracts a &quot;binder&quot; for Xelrin's quest? <br>
Is it possible that to use it as an extracter you have to actually get it from Xelrin? Could there be some hidden flags for that, so the same box could be used for 3 different quests but only work for one at a time?<br>
